description: Launched on 15/01/2019 by Currency.com team based in Gibraltar and Belarus, represents a tokenised version of traditional financial market - ETFMG Alternative Harvest ETF shares on Ethereum blockchain, price of underlined assets is tailored to Infineon Technologies AG market price. Tokenisation of the asset provides possibility to invest to popular financial markets worldwide using crypto.
name: ETFMG Alternative Harvest ETF
